{"tid":2037404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Marco Rubio：香港作為中國白手套 必須取消其獨立關稅區地位","createTime":"2020-05-27T03:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T16:14:31.000Z","uid":125168,"like":529,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"fbbedcd87fedf7339c2409ede3ae561e61eed1e7","tid":2037404,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:22:33.000Z","msg":"【🇺🇸國安法殺到｜美國國會：若中共照過惡法 即應取消香港特殊地位】<br />\n<br />\n中共執意強推國安法，已令特朗普有意啟動制裁，國會議員今日亦狂出tweet，要求國務院要企硬，當中《香港人權民主法案》推手Marco Rubio直言，一旦通過國安法，即是「一國兩制」的終結，必須取消香港獨立關稅區地位。<br />\n<br />\n對於香港作為中國白手套嘅角色，Marco Rubio亦睇得好透，批評中方一方面經濟上要「一國兩制」，但講到人權自由就玩「一國一制」。<br />\n<br />\n須知道，大陸一直利用香港「走出去」，係香港上市集資賺外匯，呢個係小粉紅吹咗幾十年但大陸制度仲係做唔到嘅嘢，而中美貿易戰亦令更多在美國上市的中國企業要回流香港，大灣區高科技發展亦要香港進口軍民兩用敏感物資。<br />\n<br />\n加上中共現時面對最大經濟下行壓力，北京成日吹要經濟保七保八，今年連GDP增長目標都唔夠膽講，連立場較親中的BBC都大大隻字話「中國夢面臨巨大挑戰」，所以一取消特殊待遇，絕對唔係京官所講「無事，唔驚」。<br />\n<br />\n大家大大力推下post<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1265437495560413184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1265437495560413184&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8UwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=a450177c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1265437495560413184&h=d13db51a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1265437495560413184</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1265383518349262848\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1265383518349262848&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8UwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=f3b9088c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1265383518349262848&h=a0e30dfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1265383518349262848</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1265469996123041797\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1265469996123041797&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8UwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=2c4a8bcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjoshuawongcf%2Fstatus%2F1265469996123041797&h=eb0cf0dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/joshuawongcf/status/1265469996123041797</a><br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n【留一口氣，點一盞燈】眾志應急資金籌募：<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/香港眾志應急資金籌募/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E6%87%89%E6%80%A5%E8%B3%87%E9%87%91%E7%B1%8C%E5%8B%9F%2F&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8UwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=9733f81b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/香港眾志應急資金籌募/</a>"},{"pid":"b334e988fe27913f037b67a590c6eb34d4ea45df","tid":2037404,"uid":283912,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:22:53.000Z","msg":"Good,快!!!!"},{"pid":"1ecd5ae64e35cb00604c99de3535132dfe93a989","tid":2037404,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e479d305b8791a1cb6f4093916cf998a335f09cc","tid":2037404,"uid":141668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:23:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a973283983858b7643ef58a9de022b2cde22cdf1","tid":2037404,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:23:21.000Z","msg":"gogogo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\